&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/056-ShivLingAshtakam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>ब्रह्ममुरारि सुरार्चित लिंगम् निर्मलभासित शोभित लिंगम्। &lt;br>
जन्मज दुःख विनाशक लिंगम् तत् प्रणमामि सदाशिव लिंगम् ॥1॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>देवमुनि प्रवरार्चित लिंगम् कामदहन करुणाकर लिंगम्। &lt;br>
रावणदर्प विनाशन लिंगम् तत् प्रणमामि सदाशिव लिंगम् ॥2॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shri Shiv Mahimna Stotram - श्रीशिवमहिम्नस्तोत्र</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shiv-mahimnstotra/</link><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shiv-mahimnstotra/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Shiva.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">श्रीशिवमहिम्नस्तोत्र 
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Shri Shiv Mahimna Stotram
&lt;div id="shri-shiv-mahimna-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#shri-shiv-mahimna-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/054-ShriShivMahimnaStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Composed by Gandharva Pushpadanta&lt;/strong> &lt;/p>
&lt;iframe width="619" height="348" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zRprEiJ06eU" title="Shri ShivMahimna Stotram" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen>&lt;/iframe>
&lt;p>॥ ॐ नमः शिवाय ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>ॐ वन्दे देव उमापतिं सुरगुरुं, वन्दे जगत्कारणम् । &lt;br>
वन्दे पन्नगभूषणं मृगधरं, वन्दे पशूनां पतिम् ॥ &lt;br>
वन्दे सूर्य शशांक वह्नि नयनं, वन्दे मुकुन्दप्रियम् । &lt;br>
वन्दे भक्त जनाश्रयं च वरदं, वन्दे शिवंशंकरम् ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shiv Tandava Stotram - शिवतांडवस्तोत्रं</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shiv-tandava-stotram/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shiv-tandava-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
