&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Shiva.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">शिवतांडवस्तोत्रं
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
