&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Shiv Tandava Stotram
&lt;div id="shiv-tandava-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#shiv-tandava-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>सामान्य गति &lt;br>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/005-ShivTandavaStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>द्रुत गति &lt;br>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/045-ShivTandavaStotramFast.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>जटाटवीगलज्जल प्रवाहपावितस्थले &lt;br>
गलेऽवलम्ब्य लम्बितां भुजंगतुंगमालिकाम्‌। &lt;br>
डमड्डमड्डमड्डमनिनादवड्डमर्वयं &lt;br>
चकार चण्डताण्डवं तनोतु नः शिवः शिवम ॥1॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>जटाकटाहसंभ्रमभ्रमन्निलिम्पनिर्झरी । &lt;br>
विलोलवीचिवल्लरीविराजमानमूर्धनि । &lt;br>
धगद्धगद्धगज्ज्वलल्ललाटपट्टपावके &lt;br>
किशोरचंद्रशेखरे रतिः प्रतिक्षणं ममं ॥2॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Daridrya Dahan Shivstotram - दारिद्र्य दहन शिवस्तोत्रम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/daridrya-dahan-shivstotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/daridrya-dahan-shivstotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Shiva.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">दारिद्र्य दहन शिवस्तोत्रम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A8-%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
