class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A8-%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Daridrya Dahan Shivstotram
&lt;div id="daridrya-dahan-shivstotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#daridrya-dahan-shivstotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/042-DaridryaDukhDahanShivStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>विश्वेश्वराय नरकार्णवतारणाय कर्णामृताय शशिशेखरभूषणाय । &lt;br>
कर्पूरकुन्दधवलाय जटाधराय दारिद्र्य दुःखदहनाय नमः शिवाय ॥ १॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>गौरीप्रियाय रजनीशकलाधराय कालान्तकाय भुजगाधिपकङ्कणाय । &lt;br>
गंगाधराय गजराजविमर्दनाय दारिद्र्य दुःखदहनाय नमः शिवाय ॥ २॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shiva Shadakshara Stotram - शिवषडाक्षर स्तोत्रं</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shiva-shadakshara-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shiva-shadakshara-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Shiva.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">शिवषडाक्षर स्तोत्रं
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Shiva Shadakshara Stotram
&lt;div id="shiva-shadakshara-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#shiva-shadakshara-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/022-ShivShadaksharaStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>ॐकारं बिंदुसंयुक्तं नित्यं ध्यायंति योगिनः । &lt;br>
कामदं मोक्षदं चैव ॐकाराय नमो नमः ॥१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>नमंति ऋषयो देवा नमन्त्यप्सरसां गणाः । &lt;br>
नरा नमंति देवेशं नकाराय नमो नमः ॥२॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shri Shivpanchaakshari Stotram - श्रीशिवपञ्चाक्षरस्तोत्रम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Shiva.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">श्रीशिवपञ्चाक्षरस्तोत्रम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Shri Shivpanchaakshari Stotram
&lt;div id="shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/023-ShivPanchaAkshari.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>नागेन्द्रहाराय त्रिलोचनाय, &lt;br>
भस्माङ्गरागाय महेश्वराय । &lt;br>
नित्याय शुद्धाय दिगम्बराय, &lt;br>
तस्मै न काराय नमः शिवाय ॥१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>मन्दाकिनी सलिलचन्दन चर्चिताय, &lt;br>
नन्दीश्वर प्रमथनाथ महेश्वराय । &lt;br>
मन्दारपुष्प बहुपुष्प सुपूजिताय, &lt;br>
तस्मै म काराय नमः शिवाय ॥२॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Uma Maheshwara Stotram - उमामहेश्वर स्तोत्रं</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/uma-maheshwara-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/uma-maheshwara-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Umamaheshwar.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">उमामहेश्वर स्तोत्रं
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Uma Maheshwara Stotram
&lt;div id="uma-maheshwara-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#uma-maheshwara-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/024-UmaMaheshwarStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>नमः शिवाभ्यां नवयौवनाभ्यां &lt;br>
परस्पराश्लिष्टवपुर्धराभ्यां | &lt;br>
नगेन्द्रकन्यावृषकेतनाभ्यां &lt;br>
नमो नमः शङ्करपार्वतीभ्यां || 1 ||&lt;/p>
&lt;p>नमः शिवाभ्यां सरसोत्सवाभ्यां &lt;br>
नमस्कृताभीष्टवरप्रदाभ्यां | &lt;br>
नारायणेनार्चितपादुकाभ्यां &lt;br>
नमो नमः शङ्करपार्वतीभ्यां || 2 ||&lt;/p>
&lt;p>नमः शिवाभ्यां वृषवाहनाभ्यां &lt;br>
विरिञ्चिविष्ण्विन्द्रसुपूजिताभ्यां | &lt;br>
विभूतिपाटीरविलेपनाभ्यां &lt;br>
नमो नमः शङ्करपार्वतीभ्यां || 3 ||&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Meenakshi Stotram - मीनाक्षीस्तोत्रम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/meenakshi-stotram/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/meenakshi-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/MeenakshiStotram.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">मीनाक्षीस्तोत्रम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Meenakshi Stotram
&lt;div id="meenakshi-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#meenakshi-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/010-meenakshiStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>श्रीविद्ये शिववामभागनिलये श्रीराजराजार्चिते &lt;br>
श्रीनाथादिगुरुस्वरूपविभवे चिन्तामणीपीठिके । &lt;br>
श्रीवाणीगिरिजानुताङ्घ्रिकमले श्रीशांभवि श्रीशिवे &lt;br>
मध्याह्ने मलयध्वजाधिपसुते मां पाहि मीनाम्बिके ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>चक्रस्थेऽचपले चराचरजगन्नाथे जगत्पूजिते &lt;br>
आर्तालीवरदे नताभयकरे वक्षोजभारान्विते । &lt;br>
विद्ये वेदकलापमौलिविदिते विद्युल्लताविग्रहे &lt;br>
मातः पूर्णसुधारसार्द्रहृदये मां पाहि मीनाम्बिके ॥ २ ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Devi Aparaadh Kshamapan Stotram - देवी अपराध क्षमापन स्तोत्रं</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/devi-aparaadh-kshamapan-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/devi-aparaadh-kshamapan-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Durga.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">देवी अपराध क्षमापन स्तोत्रं
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A7-%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A7-%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Devi Aparaadh Kshamapan Stotram
&lt;div id="devi-aparaadh-kshamapan-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#devi-aparaadh-kshamapan-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/032-DeviApradhKshamapanStotram1.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/032-DeviApradhKshamapanStotram2.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>न मन्त्रं नो यन्त्रं तदापि च न जाने स्तुतिमहो &lt;br>
न चाह्वानं ध्यानं तदापि च न जाने स्तुतिकथाः । &lt;br>
न जाने मुद्रास्ते तदापि च न जाने विलपनं &lt;br>
परं जाने मातस्त्वदनुसरणं क्लेशहरणम् ॥ 1॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shri Ganga Stotram - श्री गंगा स्तोत्रम</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shri-ganga-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shri-ganga-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Ganga.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">श्री गंगा स्तोत्रम
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%97-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%97-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Shri Ganga Stotram
&lt;div id="shri-ganga-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#shri-ganga-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/034-ShriGangaStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>देवि सुरेश्वरि भगति गंगे त्रिभुवनतारिणि तरलतरंगे । &lt;br>
शंकरमौलिविहारिणि विमले मम मतिरास्तां तव पदकमले ।।1।।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>भागीरथि सुखदायिनि मातस्तव जलमहिमा निगमे ख्यात: । &lt;br>
नाहं जाने तव महिमानं पाहि कृपामयि मामज्ञानम ।।2।।&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Ekatmaka Stotram - एकात्मता स्तोत्रं</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/ekatmaka-stotram/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/ekatmaka-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Bharatmata.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">एकात्मता स्तोत्रं
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Ekatmaka Stotram
&lt;div id="ekatmaka-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#ekatmaka-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ सच्चिदानंदरूपाय नमोस्तु परमात्मने &lt;br>
ज्योतिर्मयस्वरूपाय विश्वमांगल्यमूर्तये || १ ||&lt;/p>
&lt;p>प्रकृतिः पंचभूतानि ग्रहा लोकाः स्वरास्तथा &lt;br>
दिशः कालश्च सर्वेषां सदा कुर्वन्तु मंगलम्।। २।।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>रत्नाकराधौतपदां हिमालयकिरीटिनीम् &lt;br>
ब्रह्मराजर्षिरत्नाढ्यां वन्दे भारतमातरम् || ३ ||&lt;/p>
&lt;p>महेन्द्रो मलयः सह्यो देवतात्मा हिमालयः &lt;br>
ध्येयो रैवतको विन्ध्यो गिरिश्चारावलिस्तथा || ४ ||&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Annapurna Stotram - अन्नपूर्णा स्तोत्रम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/annapurna-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/annapurna-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Durga.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/019-AnnapurnaStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">अन्नपूर्णा स्तोत्रम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Annapurna Stotram
&lt;div id="annapurna-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#annapurna-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>नित्यानन्दकरी वराभयकरी सौन्दर्यरत्नाकरी &lt;br>
निर्धूताखिलघोरपावनकरी प्रत्यक्षमाहेश्वरी । &lt;br>
प्रालेयाचलवंशपावनकरी काशीपुराधीश्वरी &lt;br>
भिक्षां देहि कृपावलम्बनकरी मातान्नपूर्णेश्वरी ॥१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Meaning: &lt;br>
1.1: (Salutations to Mother Annapoorna) Who always give Joy to Her Devotees, along with Boons and assurance of Fearlessness (under Her Motherly care); Who is a repository of great Beauty and makes their minds beautiful by the touch of the Gem of Her (inner) Beauty, &lt;br>
1.2: Who Purifies all the Poisons and Sufferings of their minds (by the touch of Her Compassion and Bliss), and Who is the Great Goddess manifested visibly in Kashi, &lt;br>
1.3: Who Sanctified the Lineage of the King of the Mountain of Himalayas (by taking birth as Devi Parvati); Who is the Ruling Mother of the city of Kasi, &lt;br>
1.4: O Mother Annapoorneswari, Please grant us the Alms of Your Grace; Your Grace which Support all the Worlds.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Devi SidhaKunjiKa Stotram - सिद्धकुञ्जिकास्तोत्रम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/devi-sidhakunjika-stotram/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/devi-sidhakunjika-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Durga.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">सिद्धकुञ्जिकास्तोत्रम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Devi SidhaKunjiKa Stotram
&lt;div id="devi-sidhakunjika-stotram" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#devi-sidhakunjika-stotram" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>शिव उवाच
शृणु देवि प्रवक्ष्यामि, कुञ्जिकास्तोत्रमुत्तमम्।&lt;br>
येन मन्त्रप्रभावेण चण्डीजापः शुभो भवेत॥१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>न कवचं नार्गलास्तोत्रं कीलकं न रहस्यकम्।&lt;br>
न सूक्तं नापि ध्यानं च न न्यासो न च वार्चनम्॥२॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>कुञ्जिकापाठमात्रेण दुर्गापाठफलं लभेत्।&lt;br>
अति गुह्यतरं देवि देवानामपि दुर्लभम्॥३॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>गोपनीयं प्रयत्‍‌नेन स्वयोनिरिव पार्वति।&lt;br>
मारणं मोहनं वश्यं स्तम्भनोच्चाटनादिकम्।&lt;br>
पाठमात्रेण संसिद्ध्येत् कुञ्जिकास्तोत्रमुत्तमम्॥४॥&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>